# Mirrors the repo-root .gitattributes. Vercel's Root Directory for this
# project is `site/`, so a binary rule scoped here guarantees media is treated
# as binary inside Vercel's build context (preventing UTF-8/EOL re-encoding
# that corrupts MP4 bytes and destroys the moov atom).
*.mp4   binary
*.webm  binary
*.mov   binary
*.m4v   binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.webp  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf   binary
